snippet: The American women’s national soccer team star Abby Wambach’s rights were allocated to the Western New York Flash of the newly established eight-team National Women’s Soccer League.
abstract: Western New York Flash, part of the newly established National Women's Soccer League, recieves rights to Abby Wambach, star of the United States women's national team.
lead_paragraph: The American women’s national soccer team star Abby Wambach’s rights were allocated to the Western New York Flash of the newly established eight-team National Women’s Soccer League.

headline.seo: Abby Wambach to Play for Western New York Flash
headline.main: Wambach to Play at Home in Women’s Soccer League
